    - rid: 8641241821780639973
      type: {class: DialogueResponse, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        responseText: '[Wait, when you say West...]'
        nextNode:
          rid: 8641241821780639976
        dialogueTopic: 
        m_conditions: []
        alreadyDisplayed: 0
        editorPosition: {x: 4072, y: -518}
    - rid: 8641241821780639974
      type: {class: DialogueResponse, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        responseText: '[Don''t worry, I don''t mind.]'
        nextNode:
          rid: 8641241821780639977
        dialogueTopic: 
        m_conditions: []
        alreadyDisplayed: 0
        editorPosition: {x: 4072, y: -687}
    - rid: 8641241821780639975
      type: {class: DialogueNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        dialogueText: 'Look, just because she''s all shy doesn''t mean that you should
          underestimate her.

          Like all foreigners, she can be deceivingly
          cunning and mischievous if no-one puts her in her place.'
        characterEmotion: 2
        characterReaction: 2
        doesItProveAnything: 3
        responses:
        - rid: 8641241821780639978
        isRootNode: 0
        editorPosition: {x: 2501, y: 509}
        guid:
          Part1: 3554429002
          Part2: 1292925238
          Part3: 3304785556
          Part4: 2785673951
        tag: 
    - rid: 8641241821780639976
      type: {class: DialogueNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        dialogueText: ...n-no, i DON'T mean... you know... "that" West, I mean...
          um... Sorry, I have things to do.
        characterEmotion: 0
        characterReaction: 0
        doesItProveAnything: 0
        responses:
        - rid: 8641241821780639979
        isRootNode: 0
        editorPosition: {x: 4479, y: -518}
        guid:
          Part1: 2653160003
          Part2: 1118949611
          Part3: 3135390394
          Part4: 3955660051
        tag: 
    - rid: 8641241821780639977
      type: {class: DialogueNode, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        dialogueText: 'After a war like that, it shocks me that anyone could still
          care about something so insignificant.

          All I want now is to
          be able to rest without anyone thinking I''m a menace... I mean... Excuse
          me, I have to go.'
        characterEmotion: 0
        characterReaction: 0
        doesItProveAnything: 0
        responses:
        - rid: 8641241821780639980
        isRootNode: 0
        editorPosition: {x: 4447, y: -735}
        guid:
          Part1: 3008374608
          Part2: 1171127585
          Part3: 2291297185
          Part4: 217656539
        tag: 
    - rid: 8641241821780639978
      type: {class: DialogueResponse, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        responseText: '[Foreigners, huh? Then why did you hire her?]'
        nextNode:
          rid: 8641241821780639981
        dialogueTopic: 
